        "Description": "A cilent has requested a contract with a generous payout. Thus, A contract has been issued to you, 47.\r\rYour target is Gregory Walker, avid bookworm and traveler who has come all the way from the United Kingdom to Italy for a book signing and showcase event. The cilent has accused Walker of using company funds to fund his trip, after a hostile interaction about salary issues.\r\rThey have also request Catherine Lang, an inside host that has provided a ticket to Walker post-sale.\r\rGood Luck 47.",
